            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p>Per-user, per-machine licensing. There is no SaaS subscription with shared seats. If your team has three SEOs, you buy three licenses. For most users that math still works out — Sitebulb starts at $13.50/mo ($162/yr) for one user and Lumar enterprise pricing is multiples higher.</p>

        <h3>The real monthly cost most reviews skip</h3>
