        <p><strong>For any technical SEO with a site over 500 URLs: yes — buy the £199/yr (~$259) license today.</strong> Nothing else gives you the same depth of checks, JS rendering, and custom extraction in one tool. The annual cost amortises to under $22/mo. Easiest yes in SEO software.</p>

